# Platform Scope

> Surface 2 of 3. Do not edit `client/` or `mobile/MiAyudaTIC-Mobile/` UI from this workstream.

## Official paths

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `server/` | Express API → Render |
| `packages/contracts/` | `@miayuda/contracts` SSOT types |
| `scripts/smoke-*.sh` | Prod/mobile API gates |

## Standards

- Business logic in `features/<domain>/` — not `core/`
- Zod on all inputs; strict TS
- `authMiddleware` + `checkRol` on protected routes
- Dual auth: Bearer + cookie

## Contracts first

New shared types → `packages/contracts` → then server + consumers.

## Subagent

Delegate to `product-engineer-platform`.

## Skills

- `rbac-review` — auth/endpoints
- `ticket-lifecycle` — solicitud domain

## Verify

```bash
pnpm -C server run typecheck && pnpm -C server run test && pnpm -C server run build
pnpm -C packages/contracts run build   # if contracts touched
pnpm run smoke:mobile-api              # if auth/socket/media changed
```

## Never

- UI polish (delegate Design Engineer)
- Skip RBAC tests on auth changes
